    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS system. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis remains rigid with no signs of subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry is true, offering the precise feedback expected from this platform. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the drivetrain is robust and the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
